  "description": "Make her Sweet 16 absolutely unforgettable on Lake Travis! Private boat parties for 14-50 guests with DJ-quality sound, floats, and age-appropriate celebration. Every girl dreams of the perfect Sweet 16, and a Lake Travis cruise delivers beyond expectations! Give your daughter and her friends an exclusive party boat experience with swimming, floating, dancing, and memories that last a lifetime. Age-appropriate supervised fun, professional captain and crew, premium Bluetooth sound for teen music playlists, giant floats and water toys, swimming and floating (parent supervision available), BYOB for adults, soft drinks and snacks for teens, customizable party decorations, photo opportunities everywhere, safe and monitored environment, perfect Instagram moments, space for cake cutting and presents. Fleet choices: Day Tripper (14 friends, $195/hr), Me Seeks the Irony (25 guests, $295/hr), Clever Girl (50+ guests big party, $495/hr). Popular 3-4 hour format. Packages: Standard (basic party), Essentials (+$100-200/hr with party setup), Ultimate (+$250-350/hr with full party package including floats, decorations, party supplies). Book 8-12 weeks ahead for summer dates.",
